title: msg()
brief: Write a message to the status-area.
version: 0.07
seealso: alert
----

<p>The bottom row of the <span class="tt">lumail</span> mail-client is designated as the message area.</p>
<p>The <span class="tt">msg</span> function may be used to write a line of text to this area.</p>
<p>Example:</p>
<pre>
msg( "I am alive!" );
msg( "Today is " .. os.date() );
msg( 3 );
msg( false );
</pre>
